## CLI Tools

### gitmoji-cli

To use gitmojis from your command line, install [gitmoji-cli](https://github.com/carloscuesta/gitmoji-cli):

```bash
npm i -g gitmoji-cli
```

This provides an interactive client for selecting emojis when committing:

```bash
gitmoji -c  # Interactive commit
```

### gitmojis npm package

The gitmojis are also available as an [npm package](https://www.npmjs.com/package/gitmojis) for programmatic use:

```bash
npm i gitmojis
```
